Absolutely.

00:38:48.140 --> 00:38:51.250
So I hope this gave you some
understanding of the origins

00:38:51.250 --> 00:38:52.940
of print in Afghanistan,
and I look forward

00:38:52.940 --> 00:38:54.750
to any questions you might have.

