00:51:00.420 --> 00:51:04.860
Soon, people from around the world
can chime and use this material.

00:51:04.860 --> 00:51:07.480
And Elham, we look forward to
having you come and work more

00:51:07.480 --> 00:51:10.690
with our Afghan materials that are
now being processed as we speak.

00:51:10.690 --> 00:51:11.990
Thank you very much.

